{"tid":9411,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真人騷表演生含昆蟲捱轟","createTime":"2016-11-28T15:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T16:19:37.000Z","uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"feb933fa98adb6abe7add1248b9da77b662ca6a9","tid":9411,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/230439_7d5c8a42402ad32594e43f82294c06c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F230439_7d5c8a42402ad32594e43f82294c06c9.jpg&h=1615503a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國著名真人騷《I'm A Celebrity》，周日播出的一集受到觀眾猛烈批評，因為節目中兩名參加者要用口含著一些昆蟲，被猛轟是虐待動物。<br />\n<br />\n兩名參加者53歲羅伯茨（Martin Roberts）及28歲托馬斯（Adam Thomas），要接受殘酷挑戰換取食物，比賽分四個回合，主持人逐一要求兩人將蟑螂、竹節蟲、蜘蛛、馬達加斯加蟑螂等含在口中，並要維持至少30秒。<br />\n<br />\n後來的挑戰更見噁心，主持人要兩位咬爆魚眼並吐出當中汁液，而且要達到一定的容量。兩人完成後再被要求喝下有關汁液，令人反感。<br />\n許多觀眾看罷節目後大為不滿，「對不起，我無法理解為何節目利用動物作娛樂，而不受到處分。」亦有人大罵節目中的都是「病態的傻子」，連部份節目支持者亦不認同這些挑戰，覺得對動物太殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161128/55976209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161128%2F55976209&d=naVV2UsrwoB%2BRHXBd48YucW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=791dedc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161128%2F55976209&h=12587ead\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161128/55976209</a>"},{"pid":"e5bd2d3f131771cc4988ef9b84f1ec55f702ced4","tid":9411,"uid":18634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:10:28.000Z","msg":"重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fcea2a9fa5edbc06630829b7e9dee53a5302b5","tid":9411,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:18:55.000Z","msg":"而家大家到連昆蟲都要攬<img src=\